00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:52,479
In the end... JM From the Streets was RIGHT. Dyle was REAL... a Ligator grown enormous and strange, touched by something the swamp had no name for... and the conspiracy that everyone had laughed at turned out to be structurally accurate in EVERY way that mattered. Nobody thanked him. Nobody acknowledged that the loudest, most embarrassing voice in Kerning City had been pointing at a REAL threat... while the institutions around it looked away. JM demanded the creature's death anyway... out of wounded pride as much as civic concern. Dyle was slain. The swamp went quiet. And the city... which had always preferred not to look too directly at what lived below it... went back to looking the other way.
